headline: How Are Office REITs Positioned in Q4 as Demand Gathers Steam?
summary: Office demand turns positive in the second half of 2025 as leasing improves. However, BXP, CUZ, SLG and HIW head into Q4 with stabilizing vacancy and tight supply.

headline: Should BXP Stock be in Your Portfolio Pre-Q4 Earnings?
summary: BXP is set to report Q4 2025 results on Jan. 27, with revenues and FFO per share expected to rise on healthy leasing activity.
